before you test, you need
sudo apt install ssh
sudo apt install sshpass
StrictHostKeyChecking no in /etc/ssh/ssh_config
PermitRootLogin yes in /etc/ssh/sshd_config
===============================================================================================================================
run ./clean.sh first

./tpstest's input file(the example is input_example_tpstest and input_example_tpstest_remoteserver)

1st line
this computer's name ( a number )

2nd line
this computer's ip ( like 192.168.0.5 ) and a blank and this docker's ssh port ( without using docker is 22 )

3rd line
how many traders you want to create

4th line
1:create a server which will monitor the chain and write down the tps result in result.txt
0:there are no servers, in this situation, please write down 5 number A B C D E, which mean the server's ip and port(A.B.C.D:E) on another computer
1：建立一個負責監視整條chain以及把tps結果寫到result.txt的server
0：如果此程式沒有server,此時請再輸入五個數字ABCDE,代表別台的server的IP和port(A.B.C.D:E)

if there is the server:
5th line
how many computers ( or dockers ) have node

6th line
how many utxo for each trader node to issue transaction

7th line
0:use miner.sh, miner, or others method for mining
positive integer:the server will be mining and this positive integer is the block interval（second)
0:要使用miner.sh, miner, 或其他方法來挖礦
正整數:這個server會自動挖礦,此時輸入的正整數為區塊間隔時間（秒）

8th line
how many seconds you want to test tps

if you finish whole test, run ./clean.sh ( or ./docker_clean.sh ) after test
